OL,9,Fmillion already confirmed.
OL,11,FThe policy, to send migrants to
OL,12,FRwanda, is a key part of Mr Sunak's
OL,13,Fplan to "stop the boats", as he
OL,14,Fbelieves it will be a deterrent to
OL,15,Fthose crossing the Channel.
OL,17,FHowever, after legal challenges - so
OL,18,Fno migrants have been removed under
OL,19,Fthe policy.
