OL,6,FCritics said the "staggering figures"
OL,7,Freveal "the extortionate bill the
OL,8,Ftaxpayer will have to pay the Rwandan
OL,9,Fgovernment for an unworkable and
OL,10,Finhumane scheme".
OL,12,FThe government has already paid Kigali
OL,13,F#220 million under the Economic
OL,14,FTransformation and Integration Fund
OL,15,Fdesigned to support Rwanda's growth,
OL,16,Fdespite flights remaining grounded due
OL,17,Fto legal setbacks.
