OL,3,CRwanda scheme cost could soar to
OL,4,C#500m, watchdog says
OL,6,FIt was also already known that an
OL,7,Fextra #50 million was earmarked for
OL,8,Fthe partnership for next year. But the
OL,9,FNAO revealed the same sum will also be
OL,10,Fsent to Rwanda in 2025 and in 2026,
OL,11,Ftaking the cost to #370 million.
OL,13,FOn top of that, once the first 300
OL,14,Fmigrants have been relocated to
OL,15,FRwanda, ministers have agreed to put
OL,16,Fanother #120 million into the fund,
OL,17,Flifting the total to #490 million.
