OL,4,C#500m, watchdog says
OL,6,FIf they decide to leave, the UK would
OL,7,Fhalt payments for that person, but
OL,8,Fwould still give Rwanda a one-off
OL,9,F#10,000 to help facilitate their
OL,10,Fdeparture.
OL,12,FThe government has already sent Kigali
OL,13,Fan advance payment of #20 million to
OL,14,Fcover these processing and operational
OL,15,Fcosts for the first arrivals.
OL,17,FShadow Home Secretary Yvette Cooper
OL,18,Fslammed the plan after seeing the NAO
OL,19,Freport, calling it a "national
OL,20,Fscandal", which "the government is
OL,21,Ftrying to hide".
