OL,6,F"This government have a failing Rwanda
OL,7,Fscheme that has so far sent more home
OL,8,Fsecretaries to Rwanda than asylum
OL,9,Fseekers", she said.
OL,11,FThe Home Office has also already
OL,12,Fincurred direct costs of #20 million
OL,13,Fin establishing the agreement,
OL,14,Fincluding set-up charges for escorting
OL,15,Fmigrants on the one-way trip and
OL,16,Ftraining facilities, legal fees and
OL,17,Fstaff.
OL,19,FThis is expected to rise to #28
OL,20,Fmillion by the end of the year,
OL,21,Faccording to the watchdog.
